<event name="ANOMALY_CHAOS_POLICE">
    <text>The first thing you see when observing your surroundings, is a ship looking like Militia Investigator, except black like void itself, and shimmering with red and blue colors. They immediately contact you: "This is the Chaos Police Enforcer Unit. Submit yourself and your ship for inspection immediately."</text>
    <ship load="LILY_CHAOS_POLICE" hostile="false"/>
    <variable name="loc_found_anomaly" op="set" val="1"/>
    <choice hidden="true">
        <text>Continue...</text>
        <event>
            <text>"Let's see what kind of crimes have you been committing..."
The ship begins some sort of scan, and you feel an overwhelming sense of dread and unease.</text>
            <choice hidden="true">
                <text>Continue...</text>
                <event>
                    <loadEventList first="true" default="LILY_CHAOS_POLICE_NO_CRIMES">
                        <event name="LILY_CHAOS_POLICE_GNOME" req="gnome" lvl="1"/>
